/p>\n<p>那最终的理想——幸福美满的婚姻，是否幸福呢？不，你将为幸福、美好付出代价。</p>\n<p>那么，可否解脱？</p>\n<p>无美，无能，保持天真。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1683565786, "replies": 86, "id": 938436}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 202796, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3793, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 407984, "username": "stark123", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/stark123", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e383/af87/407984_mini.png?m=1556618469", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e383/af87/407984_normal.png?m=1556618469", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e383/af87/407984_large.png?m=1556618469", "created": 1556618262, "last_modified": 1556618469}, "last_reply_by": "stark123", "last_touched": 1683633071, "title": "为什么有些手机的拍照没有时间水印功能？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/938413", "created": 1683556550, "deleted": 0, "content": "苹果：我老婆的苹果手机没有这个功能\r\n华为：我的 mate30 手机，如果想在照片上留时间水印，需要每次设置一下\r\n\r\n这里表扬一下小米，设置一次，以后每次拍照，照片上就有时间水印", "content_rendered": "<p>苹果：我老婆的苹果手机没有这个功能\n华为：我的 mate30 手机，如果想在照片上留时间水印，需要每次设置一下</p>\n<p>这里表扬一下小米，设置一次，以后每次拍照，照片上就有时间水印</p>\n", "last_modified": 1683556550, "replies": 81, "id": 938413}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 55693, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are n